# Force HTTPS redirects for all domains
http://stormavenue.com/* https://stormavenue.com/:splat 301!
http://www.stormavenue.com/* https://www.stormavenue.com/:splat 301!
http://stormavenue.netlify.app/* https://stormavenue.netlify.app/:splat 301!

# Redirect www to non-www (optional - choose one)
https://www.stormavenue.com/* https://stormavenue.com/:splat 301!

# Redirect netlify subdomain to main domain (optional)
https://stormavenue.netlify.app/* https://stormavenue.com/:splat 301!
